<!-- This example requires Tailwind CSS v2.0+ -->
<div class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="lg:text-center">
            <h2 class="text-base text-indigo-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Simple Beginner's Guide</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                How to Play Exploding Chickens
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-gray-500 lg:mx-auto">
                In the deck of cards are some Exploding Chickens. You take turns drawing cards until someone draws an Exploding Chickens. Without a defuse, that person explodes and is out of the game. This process continues until there’s only 1 player left, who wins the game.

            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10">
            <dl class="space-y-10 md:space-y-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10">
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                            <!-- Heroicon name: globe-alt -->
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                            Phase 1 of Turn
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                            Choose either to pass (play no cards) or play (Play a card by placing it FACE UP on top of the Discard Pile and following the instructions on the card.
                            After you follow the instructions on the card, you can play more cards. You can play as many cards as you’d like.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                            <!-- Heroicon name: scale -->
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                            Phase 2 of turn
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                            End your turn by drawing a card from the top of the Draw Pile into your hand and hoping it’s not an Exploding Chicken. The next player then plays.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                            <!-- Heroicon name: lightning-bolt -->
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                            Ending the Game
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                            The last player who hasn't exploded wins the game. You won't ever run out of cards in the Draw Pile because there are enough Exploding Chickens to kill all but 1 player.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                            <!-- Heroicon name: annotation -->
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 8h10M7 12h4m1 8l-4-4H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-3l-4 4z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                            That's all, Good Luck!
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                            I believe in you. And unicorns too. But especially you.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </dl>
        </div>
    </div>
